_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"### Is there an existing issue that is already proposing this?\n\n- [x] I have searched the existing issues\n\n### Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe it\n\nCurrently if `ClassSerializerInterceptor` is provided globally (e.g. via `APP_INTERCEPTOR`) there is no way to provide its global options. The interceptor has an `@Optional` decorator but I guess it always resolves to `null`.\n\n### Describe the solution you'd like\n\n`ClassSerializerInterceptorOptions` should be a class, so that it can be used as an injection token to provide default options.\n\n### Teachability, documentation, adoption, migration strategy\n\nThe user can provide globally `ClassSerializerInterceptorOptions` with a class-transformer options object.\n\nIt is also possible to use or merge `ValidationPipe` options' `transformOptions` value, although that implementation would be more complicated.\n\n### What is the motivation / use case for changing the behavior?\n\nKeeping the global no-instantiation approach for providing `ClassSerializerInterceptor`, but passing global options to it.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nestjs/nest/issues/16963/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nestjs/nest/issues/16963/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nestjs/nest/issues/16813","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nestjs/nest","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nestjs/nest/issues/16813/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nestjs/nest/issues/16813/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nestjs/nest/issues/16813/events","html_url":"https://github.com/nestjs/nest/issues/16813","id":4296367152,"node_id":"I_kwDOBNMhFM8AAAABABVcMA","number":16813,"title":"Tscon